### Create customer
POST http://localhost:3000/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Riley",
  "lastName": "Adams",
  "emails": ["riley.adams@example.com"],
  "phoneNumbers": [
    { "type": "mobile", "number": "+15555550901" }
  ],
  "address": {
    "line1": "101 Main St",
    "city": "Austin",
    "state": "TX",
    "postalCode": "73301",
    "country": "US"
  },
  "privacySettings": {
    "marketingEmailsEnabled": true,
    "twoFactorEnabled": false
  }
}

### List customers
GET http://localhost:3000/customers
Accept: application/json

### Fetch customer by id
GET http://localhost:3000/customers/{{customerId}}
Accept: application/json

### Update customer
PUT http://localhost:3000/customers/{{customerId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Riley",
  "emails": [
    "riley.adams@example.com",
    "riley@example.org"
  ],
  "phoneNumbers": [
    { "type": "home", "number": "+15555550902" }
  ],
  "privacySettings": {
    "marketingEmailsEnabled": false,
    "twoFactorEnabled": true
  }
}

### Delete customer
DELETE http://localhost:3000/customers/{{customerId}}

### Download OpenAPI document
GET http://localhost:3000/api/openapi.json
Accept: application/json
